Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.69,0:00:51.53,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Written by their thirst for destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.11,0:00:54.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.99,0:00:57.66,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We searched along the rails
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:01:00.74,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Hoping to find another trail
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.95,0:01:02.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Leading to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:05.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}The heavens are waiting for motion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:07.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Fired up for action
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:08.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:09.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.63,0:01:10.46,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.46,0:01:11.17,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:11.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:12.75,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.75,0:01:14.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:17.34,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:20.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.18,0:01:24.56,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:27.10,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:29.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.40,0:01:32.61,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:41.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:46.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:51.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:54.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:56.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:57.97,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:04.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
